records.name: Dhigali Maldives - A Premium All-inclusive Resort

descriptions.direction: Located in Dhigali, Dhigali Maldives - Premium All Inclusive is on the beach. Travelers looking for local activities can try Meedhoo Harbor and Maduvvari Harbor, while those looking to experience a bit of culture can stop by The Dutch Onion Museum. Take an opportunity to explore the area for water adventures such as windsurfing.
descriptions.general: Dhigali Maldives - All-Inclusive Resort is surrounded by a large house-reef, beyond the lagoon, and is a 45-minute ride by seaplane from Male airport. Guests can enjoy the Spa set in a soothing setting of a tropical lush garden, featuring an outdoor plunge pool surrounded by day beds within the natural greenery offering indigenous therapies and healing traditions. Some rooms have a seating area for your convenience. You will find a coffee machine in the room. Every room has a private bathroom with a bath or shower and bidet, with bathrobes and slippers provided. For your comfort, you will find free toiletries. A number of activities are offered in the area, such as snorkeling and windsurfing.
